    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i cant even sleep anymore. every time i look at the news or even just look outside i just feel this massive weight in my chest. the planet is literally dying and it feels like we're all just walking around in a burning building pretending everything is fine. like what is even the point of trying to build a life or make plans when the future is just... gone? it feels so pointless to even be here.",
